hopobject.body: What do you like doing in your spare time? viagra 100mg prezzo We thought price negotiation was a huge source of friction. It also triggers an environment that pushes service providers to come up with cheaper offers, so everything is pushed to the cheapest level. We said, ‘We don’t want to do that. We’ll put a single price point to put price negotiations out of the equation.’ Then [sellers] can do five to 10 gigs an hour, and it adds up to a nice income. [Advanced Fiverr sellers can now sell gigs for more than $5.]
